\mt1 FIREMON 
\mt2 Khe Por Firemon Ndi Khergi Gap 
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare. 
\ip Firemon, ana guma bak…®me ma. KhaŇč muuŇčgiap, ana Korosi Ňčgu bak…®men guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma ma. Ana vh…®ra fhura anan Ňčgari Ňčaara guma mbe ki. Mba Ňčaara guma z…® khare, Onesimus. Ana ana thav ra vov, harigi Ňčgu bak…®men vugap, anan ki. Onesimus vov, mba Ňčgu bak…®men kav, ana maaŇč Porar h…®gap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi. 
\ip Mba tugen Por phena t…®vanen ki. Ana Ňčg…®p, Firemon gangirga tukt…®gi fhu. Ana thav, kha gava khergiap, ana Onesimus ga nd…®…®i. Onesimus mba gava ndigip, taagip wo mpiiŇčs…®ga han Ňčg…®rga. Por mba gava kherav, khaŇč Firemon ga nzuai. Ndu won Ňčaara guma ga vheg…® thari. Ndun Ňčaara guma ntigem ndava dorgap, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi. Ndu fhura taagip ana ndigirim, ana ndu phorge r…®gine farar muuŇčgip ndu han k…®ri. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Fhura Firemonan Ňčgari Ňčaara guma ana thav, ra vuga kegap, zumgum guigira Zisas khoth…®gim, Por taagia ana sarigim, ana taagia Firemon han vui. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Ef 3.1\x*Gu Por, gu Zisas Krais z…®n panan phena t…®vanen ki guma ma. Gu nza phorga guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma Timoti, Ňčka kha gava khergiap, ndu Firemon, Ňčka anan ndu ndi mbai. Ndu Ňčka phorgap Zisasan Ňčaara mbui guma ma. Ndu vh…®ra Ňčka khurkhuma vhuuŇč ma.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kor 4.17; 2 T 2.3\x*Ňäka vh…®ra kha gavar wari won mbiga h…®r…®…®Ňč Apia ndi mbai. Arkipus, ana vh…®ra nza phorgap nza Fhe Bak…®men ntara mbui gumgi kav, nza ana nzuav shogi. Nza ana nzuav kherav, nza vh…®ra kha gava ndim, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe ndu phenan phogi ga vhui, nza vh…®ra kha gavar mbe ndi mbai. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Ga 1.3\x*Nzan Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum, nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais, manin kora muumbar nde phorg…® k…®rim, nde ndavi mb…®rav wari k…®ri. 
\s1 Firemon muuŇčgi t…®var vhuuŇč Por ga muuŇčgim, Por ndikndigi. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Ro 1.8-9\x*Gu zazera wo Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, gu ndu nd…®knd…®gap, anan ndikndigi.  
\v 5 Gu khaŇč muuŇčgiap mbararagi, mbe zazera khaŇč na nzuai, ndu guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, zazera wo ndavar Zisas Krais ga nd…®…®i. Ndu won ndavar ana nd…®…®v, ndu vh…®ra zam guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ndu guigira won ndavar mbe nd…®…®i.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Fi 1.9; Kor 1.9\x*Ndu vh…®ra khurkhuman nza khuav, nza Krais khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap khueŇč nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai, ana nzan kurarim, nza guigira nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ndiv, nza vh…®ra Krais nzan kurkurav, nza nd…®…®i bigir vhuuiŇč, nza nta kaŇčgip, ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 2 Ko 7.4; 7.13\x*Ndu nan fek, ndu guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ndu won ndavar mbe nd…®…®i. Ndu mba t…®va mbuav, ndu mben ndavi havhari. Ndu mba t…®va mbuim, mba t…®v guigira na ndava mbuim, gu guigira ndikndigi. Gu guigira ndikndigap, nan ndav nan mb…®rigim, gu ki. 
\s1 Firemon taagip Onesimus ndigirim, ana ana phorge r…®gine farar muuŇčgip k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Fm 1.1\x*Gu muungen ndu vuzvugi big…®na mueŇč khare. Gu Zisas Krais z…®n pana kha bigen muun zav ndu nzuai.  
\v 9 Gu nd…®knd…®gi, gu kama havharar ndu suanga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ňäka guigira ndavar wani ga nd…®…®i t…®v, mba t…®v Ňčka kegim, Ňčka ki. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap kama m…®…®t…®gar ndu nzuai. Gu Por, gu Zisas Krais buni ndia rui guma ma. Gu mba buni ndia rui ne nzuav, gu ntigem phena t…®vanen ki.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Ko 4.15; Kor 4.9\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap Onesimusan nzuav ndun nzai. Gu phena t…®vaneŇčra kim, Onesimus zav nan h…®gi. Ana zav nan h…®gim, gu anan kurigim, ana guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®gi. Gu maaŇč ana muuŇčgim, ana guigira nan kama gegi. \f a \fr 1:10 \ft Onesimus khaŇč muuŇčgi guma ma. Ana fhura Firemonan Ňčaara guma kh…®n ki. Ana kav kav, zumgum rav Por han z…®gi. Ana z…®gap Por han kav, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, ana Zisas z…®n panan ruagi. Mbe mba tugen mben t…®v khaŇč nzuai. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, Ňčaara guma the wo Ňčgari mbasa thav, r…®…®v, Ňčg…®g…®rga, ana gari guma bak…®me, ana mba ntari ga mbui g…®…®t…®vi ga suanga, mbe mba Ňčaara guma ndiv khanarareŇč ga ntorg…®p, ana shogirim, na rimgirga. \f* 
\v 11 Ana fhum tuituigia ndun Ňčaara muuŇčgi fhuvara. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, ntigem ana guigira Ňčkan kurav Ňčaara vhuun muunga. \f b \fr 1:11 \ft Grikin kaman kha z…®, Onesimus, ana khaŇč nzuai kameŇč fara muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúŇäaara vhuuaŇč mbui.‚ÄĚ \f* 
\p  
\v 12 Gu ntige ana sarigim, ana taagia ndu han mbar vui. Gu guigira won ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgim, ana mbar vui.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Fi 2.30\x*Gu ana th…®varim, ana na han k…®rgeŇč, gu guigira nen ndikndigi. Ana na han k…®v, gu Zisas buna vhuueŇč khuav phena t…®vanen kim, ana nan kurav ndu mba mbui Ňčaara muunga.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt 2 Ko 9.7; 1 Pi 5.2\x*Gu nen muun za mbuav, gu khueŇč vuzvugi, ndu big…®n ma. Ndu na kh…®rarga, gu muunga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap ana th…®v…® thav, ana sarigim, ana ndu han mbar vui. Ana mbar vuim, gu ndu ana muunga big…®n thueŇč phorga ndu nzuai fhu. Fhuvara. Gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip nan kurkurarga nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč thueŇč k…®v, ndu wo vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®p, nan kurkurari. 
\p  
\v 15 Onesimus, ana guigira tuga t…®vaneŇčra ndu thav kegi. Ana ntige khaŇč muuŇčgim, ndu taagi ana ndigiri. Ana ntigem mbara muuŇčgip ndu phorg…® k…®rga.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 T 6.2\x*Ndu ntigem kha nd…®knd…®gar anan muuŇč thari, ana fhura ndun Ňčaara guma k…®rga. Fhuvara. Ana guigira fhura ndun Ňčaara guma k…®rga. Ndu ntigem kha nd…®knd…®gar ana muuŇčri. Ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, ana ndu phorge r…®gine fara muuŇčgi. Ndu guigira won ndavar anan n…®…®Ňčgip, Ňčko fek gu Ňčguk k…®ri. Gu nduara ana gari, Ňčka guigira fek gu Ňčguk ma. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap won ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap khueŇč kaŇčgi, ndu guigira won ndavar anan n…®…®nga. Ndu vh…®ra ana fhura ndun Ňčgar…®v muunga t…®vi, ndu guigira nta vuzvugirga. Ndu Krais z…®n panan Ňčko fek gu Ňčguk k…®v, ndu guigira won ndavar anan n…®…®Ňčgirga. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt 2 Ko 8.23\x*Ndu maaŇč muunga, ndu na gan…®nga, gu guigira ndu phorga Krais Ňčaara mbui khurkhuman vhuuŇč ma. Ndu taagip Onesimus ndigiv, ndu mba na mbui t…®vara ana muuŇčri.  
\v 18 Ana maaŇč muuŇčgip fhum big…®na mbat…®ga thuen ndun muuŇčgirga o, ana ndu Ňčgar…®gar muuŇčgirga, ana mba muuŇčgi bigeŇč, ndu ana z…® thug…®p, na z…® ndi t…®g…®ri.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Ga 6.11\x*Gu Por, gu wo farvera kha buni khergiap, ndu ndi mbai. Gu nduara ana mba muuŇčgi bigeŇč Ňčkar…®gar muuŇčgirga. Gu nduara khaŇč ndu suanga, ndu na muuŇčgi bigeŇč ma. Gu ndun tuma muuŇčgi bigeŇč ma. Gu nen ndu suanga fhu, ndu big…®n ma.\f c \fr 1:19 \ft Ndu 1 Korin 16.21 gan…®ri. \f* 
\v 20 Ndu na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi guma, ndu mbarara. Ndu Guma Bak…®me z…®n panan na suaŇčv kha t…®var vhuun muuŇčri. Ndu maaŇč nan muunga, nan ndava vhee ndikndigirga. 
\p  
\v 21 Gu guigira khueŇč kaŇčgi, ndu gu suaŇčgi buni z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap kha gava khergiap, ndu ndi mbai. Gu kaŇčgi, ndu ntigem Onesimusan muunga t…®v, ana gu khar ndu nzuai t…®v, ana guigira ana kambararga.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Fi 1.25; 2.24\x*Gu ntigem ndu phorg…® suanga buna mueŇč phorga khar ki. Mba buneŇč khare. Gu Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®gi, nde ana phorg…® suanga buni, ana nta mbarararga. Ana nde buni mbararav, na sararim, gu nde han mbar Ňčg…®g…®rga. Ndu maaŇč muuŇčgip wo phenan na suaŇčv Ňčana thuen muuŇčgirim, gu mbar Ňčg…®p, mba Ňčanen kurga. 
\s1 Por phorga Ňčgari gumgi, mbe won raar vhuun Firemon ga nd…®…®i. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Kor 1.7; 4.12\x*Khe Epafras, ana won raar vhuun ndu nd…®…®i. Ana vh…®ra phena t…®vanen ki. Ňäka vh…®ra wani t…®gap Krais z…®n panan phena t…®vanen ki.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt FG 12.12; 12.25; 13.13; 15.37-39; 19.29; 27.2; Kor 4.10; 4.14; 2 T 4.10-11\x*Khe na phorgap nza mba Ňčaara bavira mbui gumgi, Mak gu Aristarkus, Demas gu Ruk, mbe vh…®ra wari won raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i. 
\p  
\v 25 Nza Guma Bak…®me Zisas Kraisan kora muumbar nde phorg…® k…®ri.